narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: At the beginning of the year, this course was super helpful in articulating the timeline and resources available for the senior thesis! Communication for deadlines and expectations was always super clear. I felt that Anne and Collin were both readily available and eager to give advice!

Improved research skills. Namely coming up with a research question, thinking it's great, realizing it  is terrible, coming up with a new question, and repeating that process until the question is refined

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments:
The strengths include the course's organization, level of commitment and available support. 

No weaknesses!
If you want to spend a long time, researching a topic definitely do the full year

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: If youre interested in spending a long time, researching a topic do the fully thesis. Its definitely worth it.
